\c 27
\s Valsiraeri vacharangwa asi vachadzoswazve naJehovha "
\p
\v 27
\v 1 Nezuva iro Jehovha acharova nomunondo wake mukukutu, mu
\s kuru, noune simba, reviatani, iyo nyoka inokurumidza, iyo, nyoka yakagonyana; achauraya chikara chiri mugungwa.
\p
\v 2 Nezuva iro vachaimba vachiti, "Munda wemidzambiringa, chiumbira!
\v 3 Ini Jehovha ndini muchengeti wawo; ndichaudiridza nguva imwe neimwe; ndichauchengeta masikati nousiku, kuti urege kutadziwa nomunhu.
\v 4 Ini handina hasha; dai rukato neminzwa zvairwa neni! Ndaizvivamba, ndaizvipisa pamwechete.
\v 5 Kana asingadaro, ngaabate simba rangu, ayanane neni, ngaayanane neni."
\p
\v 6 Namazuva anouya Jakobho achamera midzi; Isiraeri achatunga maruva nokutumbuka; vachazadza nyika yose nezvibereko.
\p
\v 7 Ko akavarova iye sezvaakarova avo vakavarova here? Ko vakaurawa nokuurawa kwaivo vakaurawa navo here?
\v 8 Pakuvadzinga kwenyu makarwa navo nechiyero chakafanira; wakavabvisa nemhepo yake ine simba nezuva remhepo yokumabvazuva.
\v 9 Saka nenzira iyi zvakaipa zvaJakobho zvichadzikinurwa; izvi ndizvo zvibereko zvose zvokubviswa kwezvivi zvake, kana achiita mabwe ose earitari ave samabwe omunyaka akaputswa-putswa, kuti miti yakatsaurwa nemifananidzo yezuva zvirege kuzomiswa.
\p
\v 10 Nokuti guta, rakakombwa norusvingo, rasiyiwa riri roga, hwava hugaro hwasiyiwa riri dongo, serenje; ndipo pachava namafuro emhuru, ndipo paichavata pasi, ichidya mashizha apo. liKana matavi apo aoma, achavhunwa; vakadzi vachauya vachiapisa; nokuti vanhu ava havana njere; saka akavaita haangavi netsitsi navo, akavaumba haangavi norudo navo.
\p
\v 12 Zvino nezuva iro Jehovha achapura zviyo kubvira pamvura yoRwizi kusvikira parukova rweIjipiti; imi muchaunganidzwa, muchiita mumwe-mumwe, imi vana vaIsiraeti.
\p
\v 13 Zvino nezuva iro hwamanda huru icharidzwa; vakanga voparara panyika yeAsiria, navakanga vadzingirwa kunyika yeIjipiti, vachauya; vachanamata Jehovha pagomo dzvene paJerusaremu.
